wiki.content:
"Golden" continues Tyler's breakdown, with him realising what he has done (kill his friends), with him making random exclamations. At the end of the song, Tyler's therapist, Dr. TC, reveals that he is not who Tyler thinks he is, with him stating "... you're not going crazy, it's me, I'm your best friend Tyler/ I know everything, I know everything about you/ you've been helping yourself this whole time/ your friends, they're just figments of your imagination/ Dr. TC, see Tyler, I'm your conscience/ I'm Tron Cat, I'm Ace, I'm Wolf Haley, I'm ..." with Tyler then simply saying "me".
 
 Tyler has stated that he will not perform the song live
